FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FVirginia's brother Sky Roberts and his
OL,8,Fwife, Amanda, have helped spearhead
OL,9,Fthe campaign for facts and
OL,10,Faccountability surrounding Jeffrey
OL,11,FEpstein's crimes, but so far little
OL,12,Fhas been discovered about what went on
OL,13,Finside Zorro.
OL,15,FAnnie Farmer reported her abuse to the
OL,16,FFBI in 1996 - her complaint was among
OL,17,Fthe millions of documents released by
OL,18,Fthe Department of Justice earlier this
OL,19,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FYet despite the 30 years which have
OL,8,Felapsed since that brave teenager came
OL,9,Fforward to denounce her abuser, the
OL,10,Fveil of secrecy still hangs over the
OL,11,Franch.
OL,13,FNew Mexico has just launched its own
OL,14,Fbipartisan Truth Commission to
OL,15,Festablish the scope and nature of the
OL,16,Fcrimes committed by the disgraced
OL,17,Ffinancier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
