CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FIt consists of four State
OL,8,FRepresentatives (two Democrats and two
OL,9,FRepublicans) and a budget of over $2
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FGiven that it has been at least seven
OL,13,Fyears since Jeffrey Epstein was in the
OL,14,Franch, the expectation is that
OL,15,Finterviews with those who spent time
OL,16,Fat the property, especially survivors
OL,17,Fand workers, will be a more fruitful
OL,18,Fline of inquiry than a search of the
OL,19,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FThe Commission intends to produce a
OL,8,Fpreliminary report in July and a final
OL,9,Freport by the end of the year.
OL,11,FThe criminal case against Jeffrey
OL,12,FEpstein ended after his death in 2019
OL,13,Fwhen he was in prison. Following the
OL,14,Frelease of the Epstein files in
OL,15,FDecember, renewed interest in his
OL,16,Foffences led to the launch of New
OL,17,FMexican legislature's "Truth
OL,18,FCommission" and another investigation
OL,19,Fby the State's Department of Justice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
