CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FThe man who received that email was
OL,8,Fradio talk show host, Eddy Aragon.
OL,9,FAragon has relentlessly pursued the
OL,10,Ftruth behind Epstein's activities at
OL,11,FZorro, long before Epstein received
OL,12,Fwall-to-wall coverage.
OL,14,FHe forwarded the tip-off to the FBI as
OL,15,Fsoon as he received it but never heard
OL,16,Fanything back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FReceiving that email made "my blood
OL,8,Frun cold," Aragon told ITV News. He
OL,9,Ffeels confident that it came from
OL,10,Fsomeone who worked at the ranch,
OL,11,Fsomeone who had access to the house
OL,12,Fbut he has never heard again from the
OL,13,Fperson who sent the email and when he
OL,14,Ftried to send a reply, Aragon's email
OL,15,Fbounced back.
OL,17,F"What do I think happened on the
OL,18,Franch?" Eddy asks.
OL,20,F"What crimes? Underage sex, rape,
OL,21,Fforcible rape, kidnapping, murder."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
