OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FITV News has also learned that workers
OL,8,Fon the ranch were asked to sign non-
OL,9,Fdisclosure agreements, binding them to
OL,10,Fsilence or risk facing a $100,000
OL,11,Fpenalty.
OL,13,FOne man who helped to dig the basement
OL,14,Fof the ranch told us he met Epstein
OL,15,Fand immediately took a dislike to him.
OL,16,FHe said the billionaire spent money
OL,17,Ffrivolously developing the property.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
