OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FHe and other labourers scratched out
OL,8,Fthe $100,000 figure on the NDA and
OL,9,Freplaced with it $1 in protest at the
OL,10,Fgagging clause.
OL,12,FBoth he and others we approached were
OL,13,Funwilling to go on the record about
OL,14,Ftheir time at the property, where
OL,15,Fsurvivors alleged they were abused at
OL,16,Fthe hands of Jeffrey Epstein, his
OL,17,Faccomplice Ghislaine Maxwell and other
OL,18,Fhigh profile figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
