OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FA local man who nearly took a job on
OL,13,Fthe ranch is Jim Sloan. Sloan was
OL,14,Foffered a contract to excavate
OL,15,Ffoundations at the ranch, but on
OL,16,Flearning of the same NDA clause, felt
OL,17,Fit was suspicious and decided to
OL,18,Freject the work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
