OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FRumours about the nefarious nature of
OL,8,FEpstein's behaviour have swirled in
OL,9,Fthe communities near the property for
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FEzra Sage is a local firefighter who
OL,13,Fwas warned by his father as he drove
OL,14,Fpast the ranch as a little boy that
OL,15,Fthe owner of Zorro "did things to
OL,16,Flittle girls".
OL,18,FYet despite all the allegations and
OL,19,Ftestimony nothing appears to have been
OL,20,Fdone to investigate the crimes.
OL,26,@wD@TOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
