OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FA line of inquiry will be whether
OL,8,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor ever
OL,9,Fvisited the Zorro estate. It's already
OL,10,Fbeen established he visited New Mexico
OL,11,Fin October 2003, opening a new $45
OL,12,Fmillion dollar observatory at
OL,13,FMagdalena Ridge.
OL,15,FMountbatten-Windsor also had dinner
OL,16,Fwith the Democratic Governor Bill
OL,17,FRichardson, who owned Zorro before
OL,18,FEpstein and is listed on flight logs
OL,19,Fas having flown on Epstein's private
OL,20,Fjet from New Mexico to Palm Beach,
OL,21,FFlorida.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FIt is not yet confirmed however that
OL,8,Fthe former Prince visited his friend
OL,9,FEpstein at the estate. The Chair of
OL,10,FNew Mexico's Truth Commission,
OL,11,FDemocratic State Representative,
OL,12,FAndrea Romero, told ITV News "it's
OL,13,Fentirely plausible or even likely that
OL,14,Fhe that (Andrew) visited Epstein at
OL,15,Fthe ranch".
OL,26,@vD@IpmvD@Ppn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
