OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,FRomero goes on to say "it's likely
OL,8,Fthat we will ask for him to provide
OL,9,Ftestimony, whether that's voluntarily
OL,10,For by subpoena, we would like him to
OL,11,Fbe on the record and to have that
OL,12,Fconversation."
OL,14,FAndrew Mountbatten Windsor has
OL,15,Fconsistently denied any wrongdoing or
OL,16,Fknowing about Epstein's crimes.
OL,18,FRomero concedes that New Mexico's
OL,19,Finvestigations will struggle to make
OL,20,Fup for lost time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,F"Our New Mexico Department of Justice
OL,8,Fis doing something that should have
OL,9,Fbeen done long ago. We don't know
OL,10,Fanything about the extent of any
OL,11,Finvestigation having been done at the
OL,12,Franch. But we understand that that it
OL,13,Fhadn't been done until these last two
OL,14,Fweeks.
OL,16,F"The reality is we know statutes of
OL,17,Flimitations have run for many victims
OL,18,Fseeking justice in our state," Romero
OL,19,Fadds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30419
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774350340
OL,3,CMystery persists at Epstein's New
OL,4,CMexico ranch after search for human
OL,5,Cremains
OL,7,F"And if crimes happened in this state
OL,8,Fand law enforcement may have looked
OL,9,Faway if the federal government failed
OL,10,Fto do their job, if our authorities
OL,11,Ffailed to do their job, that's the
OL,12,Ftype of record the public needs."
OL,14,FDespite the many obstacles, Romero is
OL,15,Fbullish.
OL,17,F"We have a ton of allegations, records
OL,18,Fof horrible, horrible abuses that
OL,19,Foccurred at the ranch," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
